---
---
<section id="precios" class="py-16 bg-white">
  <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-secondary mb-4">Tarifas y Precios</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-500 italic text-sm italic">Transparencia y compromiso en cada sesión</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-12">
      <!-- Adultos -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-primary/30 transition-all hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M16 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0zM12 14a7 7 0 00-7 7h14a7 7 0 00-7-7z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary">Psicoterapia adultos</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">Sesión individual personalizada</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">50€</span>
          <span class="block text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">/ sesión</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Familiar -->
      <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-3xl p-8 border border-gray-100 flex items-center justify-between group hover:border-primary/30 transition-all hover:bg-white hover:shadow-xl">
        <div class="flex items-center gap-6">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-primary/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center text-primary">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197M13 7a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z" /></svg>
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary">Terapia familiar</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic">Sesión conjunta especializada</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-right">
          <span class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary">60€</span>
          <span class="block text-[10px] text-gray-400 uppercase font-bold tracking-wider">/ sesión</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Disclaimer -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border-l-4 border-gray-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 leading-relaxed italic">
        Los centros o especialistas son responsables de los precios y la información relacionada con ellos. Doctoralia no influye en los precios y no es responsable de fijarlos. Los precios son para pacientes sin aseguradora.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
